âœ… 3. âœï¸ Create a Simple Ansible Playbook

Letâ€™s create a YAML file to install Nginx or create a simple file.

vim nginx_setup.yml

â–¶ï¸ Sample Playbook:

---
- name: Install Nginx on Web Servers
  hosts: webservers
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Update APT cache
      apt:
        update_cache: yes

    - name: Install Nginx
      apt:
        name: nginx
        state: present

âœ… Save: Esc -> :wq
âœ… 4. â–¶ï¸ Run the Playbook

